title: Sarah Tate
text:
About me!
My name is Sarah Tate, and I am a third year Environmental Studies B.S. major. I am involved in Kappa Alpha Theta as Recruitment Director, and enjoy crochet and photography in my free time!


Education
University of California, Santa Barbara (2021-2025)

title: Portfolio
text:
Here is a project I am especially proud of from ES 165B: Environmental Impact Analysis.
I had to write up my own impact analysis report for a proposed housing development on Campus Point at UCSB, and evaluated how this project would impact recreational resources in and around this area!
